bdglue2.encoder.avro

Class AvroSchemaFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • bdglue2.encoder.avro.AvroSchemaFactory

  • public class AvroSchemaFactory
extends Object
    This is a factory object to provide an easy way to track and access the schema meta data that we are collecting. It is a singleton.

      • metaDataChanged

        public int metaDataChanged(DownstreamSchemaMetaData meta)
        Process the metadata for the table(s) in the meta data. Note that this method only looks for new table names and does not look for changed schema (i.e. it does not support schema evolution).
        Parameters:
        meta - contains info on all metadata, not just new or changed.
        Returns:
        the number of new tables found, or 0 if no new tablenames were found.

      • metaDataChanged

        public void metaDataChanged(DownstreamTableMetaData meta)

        Parameters:
        meta - metadata for the new or changed table.

      • getAvroSchema

        public AvroSchema getAvroSchema(String key)
        Locate the AvroSchema object associated with the table we are processing.
        Parameters:
        key - - the key to locate the schema in the hashmap
        Returns:
        null if not found, otherwise the corresponding AvroSchema.
